snippet.title: Pokémon Ruby Destiny Reign of Legends - Episode 0 - Introduction!
snippet.description:
This is a hack of Pokemon Ruby and I have decided to do a Pokemon hack so I start becoming more consistent and upload alot more frequently again so I hope you guys enjoy and make sure you let me know what starter I should pick! Also don't forget to leave a "Like" it really helps alot! :)

Download the game here!

http://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?t=102457

Want to donate any amount of money to me? Be sure if you would like to donate any amount you wish to the link below. All donations will go toward better equipment for my videos, giveaways for my awesome subscribers and also for living expenses that come with providing these videos for you. If you do not wish to donate then it's perfectly fine but anything helps. If you wish to donate anything bigger then $50.00 I will shout you out in a video and/or even invite you to do a co-commentary with me in a future Walkthrough Episode! If you donated more $50.00 please be sure to send me a PM!

https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=CP2CFXFDLMWTQ

Want to stay connected with me? Follow me on Facebook and Twitter!

Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/ZephyrSonic
Twitter - https://twitter.com/#!/ZephyrSonic See if you qualify to partner with the Curse Network

https://www.unionforgamers.com/apply?referral=v1mmkhfhqt1wgg
